        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-lg mb-6 max-w-3xl">
          When cache invalidation happens, knowing <em class="text-white">why</em> is critical. Comis uses a two-phase detection system that records pre-call state and performs post-call analysis to attribute every cache break to its root cause.
