            <p class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Lifecycle management</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Session expiry events trigger cache disposal. Orphaned caches (from crashes or disconnects) are detected and cleaned up automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-navy rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6">
